          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Never Forgotten Korean War POW Act</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for recognition of the entire period spent in a captured or missing-in-action status during the Korean War for purposes of receipt of combat pay.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-05-15T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
